      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TO PERU (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Traralgon behind Jumbuk Funi (24.21) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Top chance in this line up. PAW LYNETTE (1) finished well back at Horsham last time when a 14 length eighth (24.40) but back to the course now of her latest success. Should be about the mark. PAW GEORGIE (5) showed good speed to score (28.25) off a middle draw two back then off a similar box last time settled off pace and could manage only a 9 length 6th at this track (30.60). Great chance to atone. FOUND TREASURE (4) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
